Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很高兴但还是吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我准备的礼物也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,和大会姐一起挑的发卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也和小花名一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,生快 荣依子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 花名 小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可以给你戴上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名也来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,保佑我中限定live票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:30.92,Default - up,,0,0,0,,保佑我中限定live票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被恭喜的心情冲昏了头脑顺口就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来 小花名也来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,祝愿荣依子这一年幸福度过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,荣 荣依子?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,花名真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 小花名那么乖岂不是显得我很废啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小 小玉一点都不废哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小玉?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名真是好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名萌萌哒 敲可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇 你这怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓夹子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样老师 都快真的成夹子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你觉得趁年轻就乱七八糟的打扮就是时尚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,十年后你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是这样的 老师误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是荣依子生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,生日?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以打扮的那么喜庆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇 这是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只能感觉到恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有没有 恶意什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没想「这家伙臭显摆自己人气高」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,清瀬老师好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要直呼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 生日快乐 十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我也送你礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来 不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 这怎么看都是曲别针吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是私人物品不用还了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心意我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 不是说不用还了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上课之前把发卡全摘下来哦 夹子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了别那么叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子对榎並老师的攻势很猛烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我喜欢那种类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那种类型?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,之前呢 我对她说我毕业之后请和我交个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你毕业了的话 我也不是朋友 是恩师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真帅啊 这种样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道怎么帅但是我喜欢荣依子这种样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,冠?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 在这个时间送?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,特意这时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,特意?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那 来 帮我戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得送发卡就重复了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,特意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 冠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这戒指的尺寸和冠的无名指一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老师我带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,前段时间见到你妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让我好好照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,学校生活怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么不愉快的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,最初担心能不能融入集体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在感觉已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,感到气氛变得很柔和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是我渐渐融入了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是融入集体不如说是你们关系好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我看来是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,全班送的礼物全是发卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 你们不是商量好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样全班想法相同真是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的奇迹估计到毕业都不会再发生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,生日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,成为回忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子的发卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把修学旅行放到一边 聊我的发卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子一直戴着的那个发卡 很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很合适你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,成熟又闪亮 就是很有荣依子的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里买到的呀 说嘛说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是不想让人知道的名店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 感受到了一股不能再深究下去的压迫力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 秘密就要有保密的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,做一个谜团重重的女人就是你魅力的秘诀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠 你看行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人没有受欢迎也要有个限度的自觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都喜欢荣依子的话 我也高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 只要最后能回到我的港湾就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,演歌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说是晚上跑出去的狗 早上又乖乖回到狗窝里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,狗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,十 十仓?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就那样睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 能帮我解开这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我借一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,宿醉了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了 为什么你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 都不记得了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 好好走路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,榎并老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 榎并的学生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人才刚开始喝就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,酒量和外表的反差 很好笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 我是西村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 刚才谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.78,Default - up,,0,0,0,,啊…好 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,醉了的样子 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,榎并 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我还得去刚才的店拿落下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我来送老师她回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她住在那边的公寓 很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 到家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,开一下门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的西村看起来很像十仓呢 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大概因为是十仓本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 十仓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓是我的学生呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这个话题还没结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 十仓她可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不 并不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,直接秒答 好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓啊 她是怎么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有一点我能说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 喝水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当然要回去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我留下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是我在问你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我留下的话就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,想让你留下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我就留下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是沙发罩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喝醉了还这么挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等我睡着了要恶作剧什么的 在我脸上涂鸦什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我信不过你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好 把你绑起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出双手来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不…嗯… 各种意义上都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然全是我的错… 你也稍微反抗一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为感觉越来越有趣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有趣就可以了吗 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老师变得温驯了 哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓 你……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真是正合了你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你这算是擅自夜不归宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我联系过家里说要在朋友家过夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓你一直被绑着才对吧 什么时候联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你其实自己能解开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,酒这玩意不能喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,醉了的老师明明很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么样 你别翘课
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,回家换好衣服以后就去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老师想喝咖啡的话我来帮您冲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,先去洗脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那我顺便洗个澡行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱翻我东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不放心的话再把我绑起来?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别再提这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,明白使用方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 在家里给妈妈冲过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那对不住 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老师是不吃早饭的类型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候吃 有时候不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们一定要吃 别想靠不吃早餐节食来减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不放糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢喝黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,女高中生还这么狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老师不也喝的是黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,喝醉了被学生看护的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得挺好的 很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我差不多要回家换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,迟到的话我会毫不客气的记下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我和花名约好了要早点去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真认真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就老师来说是值得高兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,冲个澡的话时间就有点紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是有汗臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没啊 挺好闻的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,学校再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 直接回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么有种本以为稳操胜券却在最后一局被翻盘的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 一之濑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我把讲义收齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,花名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了一张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 荣依子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真啰嗦啊 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,早 上 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,别得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 十仓?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 这个 这条项链
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我昨天买的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为了打发和朋友见面之前的时间闲逛的时候看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,项链真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这颜色很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,十仓?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 十仓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,项链很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们去值日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 花名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 荣依子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 刚刚荣依子和老师说话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想你是不是遇到了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,花名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能稍微听我说几句悄悄话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,悄悄话 秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不能对别人说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不得了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,花名?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 我都站在荣依子这一边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 不是那么黑暗的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老师不是带着一条项链吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我有制作首饰的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也是自己制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢 我妈经营着杂货店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她把我制作的东西放在了店里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那老师就是买的那个?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那她知道是荣依子制作的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想应该不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果知道的话那个人应该不会戴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那就是说老师很中意它才买下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 我是第一次在现实中见到买下我制作的首饰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉
